# GRF Blank Test Pipeline
#
# Diagnostic pipeline — applies grf-blank.calqulus.yaml to Gait/Walk/Run trials.
# Outputs flat-zero Left/Right GRF series and hardware contact events only.
#
# If a blank (flat-zero) graph appears in the report:
#   → The report infrastructure works. The issue is in grf-stance.calqulus.yaml.
# If no graph appears:
#   → The report does not recognise these parameter names, or it requires
#     additional parameters (e.g. kinematic joint angles) to activate.

- template: templates/grf-blank.calqulus.yaml
  where:
    name: ^(Gait|Walk|Run)*
    force: any
